00:30:38.559 --> 00:30:44.070
I think that ultimately, what Soul Pancake,
like I said, aimed to be, this is a brand

00:30:44.070 --> 00:30:46.950
and there's gonna be a number of different
platforms from it.

00:30:46.950 --> 00:30:51.760
And I think ultimately, what we're starting
to see now, which is really cool, are Soul

00:30:51.760 --> 00:30:56.210
Pancake Meetups. 'Cause I think that talk
is cheap and anyone can get on a message board

00:30:56.210 --> 00:30:59.679
and say, "Well, I think this, that, and the
other thing." I think the harder thing is,

00:30:59.679 --> 00:31:04.679
and the most important thing, is putting it
into practice in your life.

00:31:04.679 --> 00:31:12.630
So, this is what I believe. This is what I
stand for. And getting people together in

00:31:12.630 --> 00:31:17.000
rooms. There have been people springing up
all over the country, like Soul Pancake breakfasts

00:31:17.000 --> 00:31:21.409
and stuff like that where they use the book
as a tool and talk about life's big questions

00:31:21.409 --> 00:31:24.679
and do some of these challenges together and
take it out in the real world.

00:31:24.679 --> 00:31:31.269
So, we're just trying to figure out new and
interesting ways to do that. So, that's where

00:31:31.269 --> 00:31:32.710
our--. That's where we're headed.

00:31:32.710 --> 00:31:35.690
