00:42:28.160 --> 00:42:31.450
&gt;&gt;Female Audience Member #2: So earlier you
mentioned your sort of Bohemian everything’s

00:42:31.450 --> 00:42:39.070
interconnected upbringing and I was wondering
if you had carried that forward with your

00:42:39.070 --> 00:42:44.070
son. And if so, how do you find these deeper
conversations to go with someone so young?

00:42:44.070 --> 00:42:49.589
&gt;&gt;Rainn Wilson: Yes. Well, that's an excellent
question. For my wife and I, and she's sitting

00:42:49.589 --> 00:42:57.290
right over here, the beautiful Holiday Reinhorn.
We believe very strongly in the, I'll call

00:42:57.290 --> 00:43:06.329
it the "spiritual education" of our son. And
that doesn't mean like, indoctrination into

00:43:06.329 --> 00:43:12.920
a certain way of thinking, or rote memorization
or something like that. But we do classes

00:43:12.920 --> 00:43:16.579
with local parents that are virtues-based.

00:43:16.579 --> 00:43:22.710
It's virtues-based education. So that you
learn--. So the child learns about compassion,

00:43:22.710 --> 00:43:34.000
humility, honesty, and all of these kinds
of virtues, qualities. And that's just as

00:43:34.000 --> 00:43:39.700
much an important part of his education as
arithmetic and stuff like that. We also believe

00:43:39.700 --> 00:43:44.180
in emotional education, really, like we did
ever since he was really young.

00:43:44.180 --> 00:43:48.170
Like, if he'd throw a tantrum or something
like that, we'd be like, "Oh, what are you

00:43:48.170 --> 00:43:53.089
feeling right now? Oh, you're feeling disappointment.
Oh, what's that like to feel disappointment?"

00:43:53.089 --> 00:43:59.050
And he'd be like, "I feel disappointed." And
it's like, "Oh, that's cool. I know what that's

00:43:59.050 --> 00:44:04.990
like. I feel that, too." But I think that
emotional and virtues-based spiritual education

00:44:04.990 --> 00:44:07.369
is something very missing in our schools.

00:44:07.369 --> 00:44:12.350
And I do think that's ultimately the responsibility
of parents or their faith community, or whatever

00:44:12.350 --> 00:44:16.100
community you cull together of like-minded
people.

00:44:16.100 --> 00:44:18.310
